beer.beer_description:
Double double, here comes trouble.
Please welcome Twofold, our punchy West Coast IPA rolling out that's sure to be the life of the party. 
We added all the ingredients from our classic Pale Ale recipe and then added them again, Twofold, to prove that more is more.
Along with a double dose of nostalgia, this beer delivers citrus and caramel flavours, with a refreshingly bitter finish that lets the hops do the talking.
